{
  "texts": [
    "As virtual mentors during clinical rotations, LLMs can be used to assist students in applying theoretical information to real-world circumstances by providing rapid feedback and individualized instructions to promote learning and fix misunderstandings [60].",
    "Personalized learning plans and educational materialsEducators in the medical industry face a tremendous difficulty due to the varied learning styles and needs of pupils.",
    "Several studies have demonstrated the ability of Generative AI models to adapt to an individual learners' requirements, providing personalized learning experiences [54,61].",
    "Through the utilization of AI, instructors can customize instructional content and materials to accommodate the distinct learning preferences of individual students [55,62].",
    "Students can utilize LLMs and generative AI technologies to develop study plans personalized to their own strengths, limitations, goals, and interests [11,55]."
  ]
}